{"tid":844411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普稱美墨加協議令貿易平衡 指美國不急與中國談判","createTime":"2018-10-02T00:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T00:51:21.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"605f0201c59a944e4c3fd95c0a1e0c6d15c408c7","tid":844411,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:44:13.000Z","msg":"特朗普稱美墨加協議令貿易平衡 指美國不急與中國談判<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%A2%A8%E5%8A%A0%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E4%BB%A4%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1-%E6%8C%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%A5%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4-181155053.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25A1%25A1-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AB%2587%25E5%2588%25A4-181155053.html&d=P1GZ2xwQnzPT8eOpEw7DJ8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7bbf1b72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%A2%A8%E5%8A%A0%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E4%BB%A4%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1-%E6%8C%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%A5%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4-181155053.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國與加拿大在最後限期前，達成新的貿易協定，與墨西哥組成「美墨加協議」，取代有多年歷史的「北美自由貿易協定」，預計新協議在11月底簽署。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普會見記者時說，「美墨加協議」是最新的平衡貿易協定，對三國都有利，又說美國向外國貨品加徵重關稅的政策，發揮功效，令其他國家願意重新談判有損美國利益的貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">特朗普提及中美貿易戰，表示自從兩度向中國貨品加徵關稅後，中方十分渴望與美國展開談判，但美國不急於與中方談判，認為現時並非時機。他說兩國長年的貿易差距，並非中國的錯，而是美國前政府坐視不理。</span>"},{"pid":"a1a1e0fd91581528119b973a541e7a092f344b7e","tid":844411,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:46:42.000Z","msg":"想投降?睇下我心情先啦"},{"pid":"8f49764a6a5fd8f309e758372b985d0627db1464","tid":844411,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:47:29.000Z","msg":"✌🏻"},{"pid":"0b9f1de0cce6fe45515b2bb99dbedb4dd6827ca2","tid":844411,"uid":165012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:49:38.000Z","msg":"依家講埋出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58035e3f9fd283c934fa93944e0a7017cf8fc74","tid":844411,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T00:51:21.000Z","msg":"抽鳩黑馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}